\mt1 1 KORIN 
\mt2 Khe Por Fharav KoriniŇč Ndi Khergi Gap 
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare. 
\ip Por kegi tugen, Korin ana Akaia fhain Ňčgu bak…®me ma, ana Grik fhain ki. Por ana fharav Zisas buni vhuuiŇč bun Korin Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, Korinan sios khavgi guma ma. 
\ip Por maam mbe han sios khavgiap, ana mbe thav, harigi Ňčanen vugim, simt…®k Korin siosir h…®gi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap Por kha gava khergiap, mbe nd…®knd…®gir mben n…®…®Ňčv vh…®ra mben simt…®gi, ndi th…®gar maan zav kha gava khergiap mbe ndi mbarigi. Por Korinan kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Ana kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe muuŇčv k…®v guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k mbe fhura ana kueg…®rim, ana korgi Ňčgirg…® rivgi. Ana vh…®ra mben t…®vir vhuuiŇč vh…®ra mbat…®girga nen rivgi. Por mba mani gu mburi muunga t…®vir vhuuiŇč ana nta nzuai. Ana vh…®ra, mba gumgi mbe fhura Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara gan…®rim, ana mbe gan…® thagim, mben hi simt…®gi ana nta nzuai. Ana vh…®ra mbe Fhe Bak…®me rotur muunga t…®vi gum Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar fhura guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ana mbe nd…®…®i nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ana nta nzuai. Ana vh…®ra gumgi vh…®zav taagia khavi ne nzuai. 
\ip Kha bigi, nta zam simt…®gir KoriniŇč ga nd…®…®i. Por mben kurarim, mbe guigira Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgira buni vhuuin mbe nzuai. Kha gavar guigira khuen mbe kh…®vigi. Ana mbe guigira harigi gumgi gu mbigi vuzvug…®p wari wo ndavir mben n…®…®nga t…®var mbe kh…®vigi. Mba t…®v, ana fharigi nd…®knd…®gar vhuuiŇč ma, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar fhura ana Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe fhura ntari gu ruur muuŇčv, wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkua thari. 
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt FG 9.14; 18.1; 18.17; Ro 1.7; 10.12; 1 Ko 6.11; 2 T 1.9\x*Gu Por, gu Krais Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara guma mbe ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugar, ana na ndi fagi. Gu nza wari t…®gap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma Sostenes, Ňčka kha gava khergiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi, nde Korin Ňčgu bak…®men ki siosar ki. Ňäka mba gavar nde ndi mbai. Krais Zisas, ana Ňčgaravra k…®r zav nden kamgiap, ana nden wora mbuigi. Ana za kha Ňčguir nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais z…®n rotu mbuav, ana z…®n Fhe Bak…®men kaav ana phorga nzuai gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben nde phorgap wora mbuigi. Ana mbe Bak…®me gum, ana vh…®ra nza Bak…®me ma.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ro 1.7; 2 Ko 1.2\x*Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais fhura nde kora muuŇčv, ndava m…®…®t…®gar nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde k…®ri. 
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigap ana phorga nzuai. 
\p  
\v 4 Nde Krais Zisasan phorga kim, Fhe Bak…®me fhura nde kora mbuav, t…®vir vhuuin nde mbuim, gu ne nzuav zazera wo Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav anan ndikndigi.  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 1:5-6 \xt 1 Ko 2.1-2; 12.8; 2 Ko 8.7; 2 T 1.8; VB 1.2\x*Gu khueŇč nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ana ndikndigi. Nza fhum Kraisan buna vhuueŇč bun nde suaŇčgim, ne khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, nden ndavi vherir ki. Nde Zisas phorga kim, maaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me za kha bigir nde n…®…®Ňčgi. Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra nden kurkurigim, nde tuituigiap anan buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav, nde vh…®ra anan Ňäina Ňäaar Ňčgari bigi, nde tuituigira nta kaŇčgi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Ru 17.30; Fi 3.20; 2 Te 1.7; Ta 2.13; 2 Pi 3.12\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde nza wari wo Bak…®me Krais Zisas za k…®rar h…®rganen rarga kav, nde ntigem za Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar fhura nd…®…®i nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč gum ŇčkasŇčkagi ndigap, nde nd…®knd…®gi gum ŇčkasŇčkagi ga nzuav tivgi fhuvara.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Fi 1.6; Kor 1.22; 1 Te 3.13; 5.23\x*Zisas Krais nden kurarga, nde havhargip k…®v k…®rim, ana taagip zir…®rga tuk h…®g…®rga. Nde mba nza Bak…®me Krais Zisas h…®rga tugar, nde mba tugen, nde Fhe Bak…®me n…®man, simt…®k thueŇč k…®rga fhu.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ais 49.7; Zo 17.21; 1 Ko 10.13; 1 Te 5.24; 1 Zo 1.3\x*Fhe Bak…®me, ana won Kam Zisas Krais phorg…®p ndava bavira k…®r zav nden kamgi. Ana nza Bak…®me ma. Fhe Bak…®me mba suaŇčgi bigi, ana zam ntan muuŇčgirga. 
\s1 Sios sh…®geregi. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Ro 12.16; 2 Ko 13.11; Fi 2.2; 3.16; 1 Pi 3.8\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, gu nza wari wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais z…®n, gu kama havharar khaŇč nde nzuai. Nde mba nzuai buni, nde wari t…®g…®p ndava bavira k…®v, mba buni suaŇčri. Nde wari sh…®g…® su thari. Nde guigira wari t…®g…®ra k…®v, nd…®knd…®ga bavira muuŇčv, wari t…®g…®p vuzvuga bavira k…®ri.  
\v 11 Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, Krowe phorga ki gumgi mbari, mbe khaŇč na nzuai. Nde wari ga vhegap, wari sh…®ga sui t…®v nden r…®gar ki.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Zo 1.42; FG 18.24-28; 19.1; 1 Ko 3.4\x*Gu mba t…®vi ga nzuai. Nde mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Por nt…®…®ri ma.‚ÄĚ Nde mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Aporos nt…®…®ri ma.‚ÄĚ Nde mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Pita nt…®…®ri ma.‚ÄĚ Nde mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Krais nt…®…®ri ma.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Ram muuŇčgi t…®vi mbare? Ee, Krais, ana r…®g…®ra wo sh…®ga suegire? Ee, gu Por, gu nden kurkura zav nde nzuav khanararen rimgire? Ee, nde Por z…®n panan ruagire? Fhuvara!  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt FG 18.8; 19.29; Ro 16.23\x*Gu khuen ndikndigi. Gu nden r…®gar, gu Krispus gum Gaiasra ruagi. Gu harigi gumgi thari ruagi fhuvara. Gu ne nzuav, gu Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigi.  
\v 15 Gu khuen ndikndigi, guma the ntigem khaŇč suanga fhu, ‚ÄúGu Por z…®n panan ruagi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Ko 16.15\x*Gu vh…®ra Stefanas gum ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, gu mbe ruagi. Gu vh…®ra harigi nt…®…®ri, ruagi thi? Gu kaŇčgi fhuvara, gu nd…®knd…®k Ňčangi.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 28.19; Zo 4.2; 1 Ko 2.1; 2.4; 2.13; 2 Pi 1.16\x*Krais, ana won z…®n panan gumgi ruar zav na farasarigi fhuvara. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ndikndigi. Ana wo buna vhuueŇč bun suan zav nan farasarigi. Gu ana buna vhuueŇč, gu kha nuianan nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kav buni nzuai t…®vi z…®n vov ne bun nzuai fhuvara. Gu kha nuiana gumgi nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kav buni nzuai t…®vi z…®n vov anan buna vhuueŇč bun suanga, Krais mba rimgi khanarareŇč ne ŇčkasŇčka, ne fhura ki ne ma. 
\s1 Krais, ana Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka gum nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč ma. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt FG 17.18; Ro 1.16; 1 Ko 2.14; 15.2; 2 Ko 4.3\x*KhueŇč guigira, k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segap Ňčgu mbat…®gar Ňčg…®rga t…®vi ga mbui gumgi, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Krais rimgi khanarareŇč bun nzuai kameŇč, mbe fhura ŇčanŇčangia nzuai kameŇč ma. Nza Fhe Bak…®me taagia nza ndigi gumgi gu mbigi, nza kaŇčgi, Krais rimgi khanarareŇč bun nzuai kaman vhuueŇč, ne Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka ma.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Ais 29.14; Jer 8.9\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu mba nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki gumgi, gu mbe nd…®knd…®gir vhuuin muuŇčgirim, mbe nduarira nta gan…®nga, nta fhura ki nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč ma. Gu vh…®ra mba bigi kaŇčgi gumgi, gu mbe nd…®knd…®gir muuŇčgirim, nta big…®n then muuŇčgirga, tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Jop 12.17; Ais 19.12; 33.18; 44.25; Mt 11.25; Ru 10.21; Ro 1.20-21; 1.28\x*Nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki gumgi maaŇč ki? Moses suaŇčgi t…®vir vhuuiŇč sure muuŇčgi gumgi maaŇč ki? Kha nuianan nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kav ŇčkasŇčkagiap buni nzuav harigi gumgi buni daasuav mbe kambai gumgi maaŇč ki? Fhe Bak…®me kha nuianan gumgir nd…®knd…®gi gum mbe nzuai buni, ana za nta mbuim, nta fhura sh…®ksh…®gap tamtam nzuai buni ma. 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Mt 11.25; Ru 10.21; Ro 1.20-21; 1.28\x*Kha nuiana gumgi, mbe won nd…®knd…®gir vhuuin panan, mbe Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me taagia kha nuianan ki gumgi ndir zav harigi khesharigi tuav ga muuŇčgi. Nza Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nzuaim, kha nuiana gumgi khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMbe fhura sh…®sh…®ga nzuai buna vhuueŇč ma.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuai buna vhuueŇč, nza ne bun nzuaim, ne mbararav ne khoth…®gi gumgi, Fhe Bak…®me taagia mbe ndirganen ndikndigi.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Mt 12.38; Mk 8.11; Zo 4.48; FG 17.18; 17.32\x*Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap mirikori gan…®v nta khothiv…® za mbui. Mbe GrikiŇč, mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kaŇčgir za mbui.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Ais 8.14; Mt 11.6; Zo 6.60; 6.66; Ro 9.32; 1 Ko 2.14; Ga 5.11\x*Nza Krais khanarareŇč ga ntorgap rimgim, nza ana bun nzuaim, mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe ne mbararagim, ne mbe nd…®knd…®gir buna mbat…®geŇč ma. Mbe GrikiŇč, mbe kha nd…®knd…®gar mba buna vhuueŇč ga mbui, ne fhura ŇčanŇčanav tamtam nzuai buneŇč ma.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Ro 1.4; 1.16; 1 Ko 1.18; Kor 2.3\x*Nde nza Fhe Bak…®men nzan kamgi nt…®…®ri, nde ZudaiŇč gum, nde GrikiŇč, nza wari t…®g…®ra nza kaŇčgi, Krais, ana Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka gum ana nd…®knd…®gar vhuuŇč ma.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt 2 Ko 13.4\x*Kha nuiana gumgi, mbe wari won nd…®knd…®gira kha nd…®knd…®gar Fhe Bak…®me mbui, ana nd…®knd…®gi mbari ŇčanŇčangiap, mben nd…®knd…®gi kambarigi fhuvara. Mbe mba nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui, nta guigira nd…®knd…®gi guari fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®men nd…®knd…®gi nta guigira mben nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kambarigi. Mbe vh…®ra kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčkagi mbari gari, nta ŇčkasŇčka ki fhu. Mbe fhura maaŇč nzuai. Anan ŇčkasŇčkagi, nta guigira ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me kav, ntan ŇčkasŇčka guigira gumgir ŇčkasŇčka kambarigi. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Mt 11.25; Zo 7.48; Ze 2.1-5\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde mba Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgim, nde ndavi domdorgiap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, nde mba tuge nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Nde vh…®rve, nde kha nuiana gumgi r…®mgi n…®man, nde nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kaŇčgi gumgi fara muuŇčgi fhuvara. Nde vh…®rve, nde z…®ri bak…®vi ki fhuvara. Nde vh…®ra, nde vh…®rve, nde z…®ri ki fhuv ndegi gu ndegmbori nde tegi.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Mt 11.25; Ze 2.5\x*Fhe Bak…®me, ana gumgi garav khaŇč nzuai gumgi, ‚ÄúKhe ŇčanŇčangi gumgi khare.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuai gumgi, ana mbe farasav, mbe ndiav, ana mem…®rar mba khaŇč nzuai gumgi ga nd…®…®i, ‚ÄúNza guigira nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki.‚ÄĚ Ana mba gumgi khaŇč nzuai gumgi, ‚ÄúMbe z…® ki fhuv gumgi ma.‚ÄĚ Ana mbe maaŇč nzuai gumgi, ana mbe farasav mbe ndiav, ana mem…®rar mba z…® ki gumgi ga nd…®…®i.  
\v 28 Ana kha nuianan z…® ki fhup gumgi, ana mbe ndiav, mbe farasi. Mba gumgi, mbe harigi gumgi mbe garim, mbe z…®ri ki fhu, mbe big…®n then muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana maaŇč mbuim, mba z…®ri kav ŇčkasŇčka ki gumgi, mbe z…®ri fhura kora verav, mbe z…®ri ki fhuv gumgi fara muuŇčgiap gumgi kh…®ni fara muuŇčgiap ki.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt Ro 3.27; Ef 2.9\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, guma the ntigem Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man wo z…® ndiv vun kuarga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 1:30 \xt Jer 23.5-6; Zo 17.19; 2 Ko 5.21\x*Fhe Bak…®me nduara nde ndigap Krais Zisas phorgi. Ana Krais ndi t…®gi, ana nzan nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin n…®…®Ňčge ma. Fhe Bak…®me Kraisan panan, ana nza muuŇčgim, nza t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi kav, nza ana vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n vui. Nza Krais muuŇčgi Ňčaara panan Fhe Bak…®me taagiap nza vhezgiap, nza ndigim, t…®vi mbat…®gi wom nza gari fhu.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 1:31 \xt Jer 9.23-24; 2 Ko 10.17\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me khuen muungen nza vuzvugi. Ana buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma ana ndikndig…®r za mbui, ana Fhe Bak…®me ana muuŇčgi Ňčaarara ndikndig…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\c 2  
\s1 Por KoriniŇč Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va nzuai. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Ko 1.17\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde na nd…®knd…®g…®. Gu nde han z…®gap, gu Fhe Bak…®me buni, gu nta bun nde nzuav, gu mba bigi kaŇčgi gumgi mba buni bak…®vi nzuai mbugum nde suaŇčgi fhuvara. Gu mbe nzuai suambarar nde muuŇčgi fhuvara.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Ga 6.14; Fi 3.8\x*Gu nde r…®gar kav, gu harigi big…®n the nzuai fhuvara. Gu Zisas Kraisra nd…®knd…®gi. AhaŇč, Zisas Kraisra, ana khanarareŇč ga ntorgap, rimgi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt FG 18.9; 2 Ko 10.1\x*Gu nde phorga kav, gu ŇčkasŇčka ki fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gu rivgiap, nin…®k na mbuim, gu ki.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Ro 15.19; 1 Ko 1.17; 1 Te 1.5; 2 Pi 1.16\x*Gu nde nzuai buni gum, gu nde suaŇčgi, gu kha nuianan ki nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kaŇčgi gumgi nde nzuai fara muuŇčgiap, nde nzuai fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaarar ŇčkasŇčka gu nzuai bunin nde kh…®vi, nde kaŇčgi, gu nde suaŇčgi buni, nta guigira buni ma.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 2 Ko 4.7; 6.7\x*Gu khueŇč nzuav maaŇč muuŇčgi. Gu guma nd…®knd…®gar nde nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, nde Zisas khothiv…® thagi. Gu vuzvugi, Fhe Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčka nduara nde nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, nde Zisas khoth…®g…®rga. 
\s1 Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nd…®knd…®ga vhuun nza nd…®…®i. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt 1 Ko 1.28; Ef 4.13; Fi 3.15; Hi 5.14\x*Gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n vov, th…®ga havhargi. Nza bun nzuai buna vhuueŇč, mbe nta mbararav, nta kaŇčgi. Mbe mba kaŇčgi nd…®knd…®gi, nta kha nuianan ki gumgi ŇčkasŇčkagir nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč fhuvara. Nta vh…®ra kha nuianan ki gumgir panin nd…®knd…®gi fhuvara. Mba gumgir pani, mbe za mbat…®gi mbe Ňčgu mbat…®gar Ňčg…®r za mbui nt…®…®ri ma.  
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 2:7-8 \xt Ro 16.25-26; Ef 3.5; 3.9; Kor 1.26; 2 T 1.9\x*\x - \xo 2:7-8 \xt Ru 23.34; Zo 7.48; FG 13.27; 2 Ko 3.14\x*Nza Fhe Bak…®me zorga ki nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč, nza nta bun nzuai. Fhe Bak…®me zumgum kha nuiana muuŇčgi. Ana fhum wo nd…®knd…®gar, nza nzuav tuav ga muuŇčgi, nza ana han Hevenan mpirmpir…®ga vhuun muunga. Mba mpirmpir…®gar vhuun kameŇč zorga ki, kha nuiana guman pana the ne kaŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe ne kaŇčgia kake, mbe Heven gari Guma Bak…®me, mbe ana ndi khanarareŇč ga t…®ga fhuge nt…®…®Ňč.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Ais 64.4\x*Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuaim, nza ne bun nzuai, ‚ÄúMba bigi, guma the fhum nta gangiap, ntan kameŇč mbararagi fhuvara. Guma the vh…®ra mba bigi ga nd…®rigi fhuvara. Mba bigi, guigira wari wo ndavir Fhe Bak…®me n…®…®Ňčgi gumgi, ana mbe nzuav mba bigi bevahegim, nta ki.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Mt 13.11; 16.17; Zo 14.26; 1 Zo 2.27\x*Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mba bigin nza kh…®vigim, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap nta kaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar, Fhe Bak…®me mba zorga ki nd…®knd…®gi, ana nta ndi gari.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Snd 20.27; Jer 17.9; Ro 11.33-34\x*Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, harigi guma the harigi guma the nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mba guman vhen ki guma, ana nduara ana nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra mba t…®vara muuŇčgi. Guma the Fhe Bak…®men nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar, ana nduara ana nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Zo 16.13-14\x*Nza kha nuianan ki gumgi nd…®knd…®gi nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vov, Fhe Bak…®men nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza Fhe Bak…®me han kega zergi Ňäina, ana nzan vhen ki. Ana nza vhen kim, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana fhura nza n…®…®Ňčgi bigir vhuuiŇč, nza nta kaŇčgi.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Ko 1.17; 2.4; 2 Pi 1.16\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba bigir vhuuiŇč, nza nta bun nzuav, nza kha nuiana guma the nza kh…®vigi nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč, nza nta bun nzuai fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nza kh…®vigi buni, nza nta bun nzuai. Nza Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara buni vhuuiŇč, nza nta bun Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar vhen ki gumgi, nza ntan mbe kh…®vi. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Mt 16.23; Zo 8.47; 14.17; Ro 8.5-7; 1 Ko 1.18; 1.23\x*Guma Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ki fhu, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar fhura nd…®…®i nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč, ana nta kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, mba bigi nta fhura ŇčanŇčangi bigi ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ki gumgi, mbera mba nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ga nd…®knd…®g…®p nta kaŇčgirga.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Te 5.21; 1 Zo 2.20; 4.1\x*Guma Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ki, ana bigi mbararav, nta nd…®knd…®gi. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ki guma, guma the ana mbui t…®vi gan…®v, nta suaŇčv ana suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Jop 15.8; Ais 40.13; Jer 23.18; Zo 15.15; Ro 11.34\x*Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúThe Guma Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi? The maaŇč muuŇčgip nd…®knd…®gi tharir ana kh…®v…®rie?‚ÄĚ Nzara Krais nd…®knd…®k nzan ki. 
\c 3  
\s1 Siosan Ňčaara guma, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara guma ma. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Zo 16.12; 1 Ko 2.14-15\x*Nde guigira na phorgap Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, gu fhum Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nde nzuav, gu Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara z…®n vui gumgi ga nzuai mbugum nde suaŇčgi fhuvara. Gu ndava vura t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi ga nzuai suambarar nde muuŇčgi. Mba tugen nde tarire fara muuŇčgi, nde ntigar Kraisan t…®vi z…®n vui.  
\v 2-3 \x - \xo 3:2-3 \xt Zo 16.12; 1 Ko 1.10-11; 11.18; Ga 5.20-21; Hi 5.12-14; Ze 3.16; 1 Pi 2.2\x*Gu nde nd…®…®i buni, nta ta fara muuŇčgi. Gu tan nde nd…®…®i. Gu mban havhar…®r nde nd…®…®i fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde mba tugen, nde mban havhar…®r mb…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde ntigem vh…®ra, nde mban havhar…®r mb…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde ndavi vuri t…®vi z…®n vuavra ki. Nde panara thav wari garav, wari daav, wari shogavra ki. Mba t…®vi, nta ndava vura t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi mbui t…®vi fhuv thi?  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Ko 1.12\x*Nden gumgi mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Por z…®n vui.‚ÄĚ Nde mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Aporos z…®n vui.‚ÄĚ Nde mba khesharigi buni nzuav, nde kha nuiana gumgi mbui t…®va mbui fhuv thi? 
\p  
\v 5 Ee, Aporos z…® bak…®me kire? Ee, Por z…® bak…®me kire? Ee, nza zam fhura Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara gumgi kim, ana nzan kurkurigim, nde Zisas khoth…®gi. Nza bevbevira, nza zam Fhe Bak…®me nza n…®…®Ňčgi Ňčaari, nza nta mbui.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt FG 18.4-11; 18.24-28; 19.1; 1 Ko 1.30; 2 Ko 3.5; 10.14-15\x*Gu nde suaŇčgi bunin vhuuiŇč, nta khaŇč muuŇčgi, gu mban vh…®ga mp…®rigi. Aporos zav mb…®n ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Fhe Bak…®me, ana nduara mba mban vh…®ga muuŇčgim, ana vhuuŇčgiap mba tegi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 2 Ko 12.11; Ga 6.3\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba mban vh…®gi pargi guma, ana fhura ki ne ma. Mba mb…®n nta n…®…®Ňčgi guma, ana vh…®ra fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®me, ana nduara mba mba muuŇčgim, nta mba tegi, ana nduara z…® ki.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Ro 2.6; Ga 6.4-5; VB 22.12\x*Mba mban vh…®gi pargi guma gum, mb…®n nta n…®…®Ňčgi guma, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Mani vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaara muuŇčgi. Mani won Ňčaara muuŇčgi ne suaŇčv, mani won Ňčaara tug…®ra t…®g…®p, wani won vheza ndirga.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Mt 13.3-9; FG 15.4; 2 Ko 6.1; Ef 2.20-22; Hi 3.3-4; 1 Pi 2.5\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Ňčka fhura Fhe Bak…®me phorga Ňčgari gumani ma. Nde Fhe Bak…®men m…®ni fara muuŇčgi. 
\s1 Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara guma, ana pheni ga mbui guman fara muuŇčgi. 
\p Nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me phena fara muuŇčgi. Ana nde muuŇčgim, nde ki.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Ro 15.20; 1 Ko 4.15; 15.10; 1 Pi 4.11; 2 Pi 3.15; VB 21.14\x*Fhe Bak…®me kha Ňčaara muunga nd…®knd…®gar na n…®…®Ňčgim, gu guigira pheni ga mbui Ňčk…®…®ra guma fara muuŇčgiap, gu fharav mba phenan muunga k…®ni havhari ndi suegi. Gu nta ndim suegim, harigi guma mbe zav, mba k…®ni t…®n mba phena muuŇčgi. Nde gumgi bevbevira, nde zam tuituigira wari wo mbui pheni Ňčk…®…®ri gan…®ri.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Ais 28.16; Mt 16.18; 2 Ko 11.4; Ga 1.7; 1 Pi 2.4-6\x*Nde khueŇč kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me Zisas Krais ndim mba phenan r…®ga kuaŇč kh…®ngi. Guma the ana sig…®p harigi r…®ga kuaŇč the ndi kh…®ngip, ana t…®n mba phenan muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 12 Fhe Bak…®me ana ndim, mba phena r…®ga kuaŇč kh…®ngim, gumgi anan t…®n phena mbui. Mbe gumgi mbari, mbe gorar phena mbui. Mbe mbari sirvar phena mbui. Mbe mbari, mbe vhez vun ndagi Ňčk…®…®ar phena mbui. Mbe mbari khirar phena mbui. Mbe mbari, mbe tugi suagiap, phena mbui. Mbe mbari wit hari ndigap phena mbui.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ru 2.35; 1 Ko 4.5; 2 Te 1.7-10; 1 Pi 1.7; 4.12\x*Mbe maaŇč mbui, zumgum Fhe Bak…®me za khaŇč nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tuga sarigi. Mba tugar, mbe mba mbui Ňčaari, nta za k…®rar heg…®rga. Mba tuk, ana vhava farar muuŇčgip h…®g…®p, za mba gumgi muuŇčgi Ňčaari, ana nta shiv, ntan pan…®nga, mbe Ňčaari vhuuiŇčra muuŇčgi o, fhu.  
\v 14 Guma, ana kha r…®ga kuan kuamkuav phenan muuŇčgirga, ana phen shigirga fhu, mba Ňčaara guma, ana won vheza ndirga.  
\v 15 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Ňčaara guma the, anan Ňčaar za shigirga, mba guma muuŇčgi Ňčaari za vh…®zgirga. Mba guma, ana vhava r…®gap shigim, mbe taagia ana ndigi guman farar muuŇčgip k…®rga. 
\s1 Nde Fhe Bak…®me phen ma. 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Ko 6.19; 2 Ko 6.16; Ef 2.21-22; Hi 3.6; 1 Pi 2.5\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me phen ma. Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar nden vhen ki. Nde ne kaŇčgi fhuve?  
\v 17 Guma the Fhe Bak…®men phenan farfagirga, Fhe Bak…®me mba guman farfagirga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi phen, ana ana phen ma. Fhe Bak…®men phen, ana Ňčgaravra ki. Ndera ana phen ma. 
\s1 Nza gumgi z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuarga fhu. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Snd 3.7; Ais 5.21\x*Nde nduarira wari guiguig…® thari. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde r…®gar guma the kha nuiana bigi, ana zam nta kaŇčgip, kha nd…®knd…®gar won muunga, ‚ÄúGu guigira nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč ki.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč nzuaim, ana fharav bigi kakagi guma ga geg…®p, keg…®p, ana guigira bigi kaŇčgi guma k…®rga.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Jop 5.13; 1 Ko 1.20; 2.6\x*Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, kha nuianan nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč, Fhe Bak…®me nta garim, nta ana r…®mani n…®man, nta ŇčanŇčangi t…®vi ma. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč mba t…®vi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúGumgi mbari, mbe mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir harigi gumgir muunga nd…®knd…®gi ki. Fhe Bak…®me mben t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuim, nta wom mbera farfagi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Sng 94.11\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap vh…®ra kha kameŇč ki, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ana mba bigi kaŇčgi gumgi, ana mben nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi. 
\q1 Ana mbe muun za nd…®knd…®gi nd…®knd…®gi, ana za nta kaŇčgi, nta fhura ki nd…®knd…®gi ma.‚ÄĚ 
\b  
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt 1 Ko 1.12; 3.4-6; 2 Ko 4.5; 4.15\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde mba gumgi z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi t…®v, nde ana thari. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mba gumgi gum mba bigi, nta zam nde nt…®…®ri ma.  
\v 22 Por, gu Aporos, Pita, kha nuian, nde ntigem khar ki, nde rimgirga zumgum h…®rga bigi, mba bigi, nta zam nden nt…®…®ri ma.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Ro 14.8; 1 Ko 11.3; 2 Ko 10.7; Ga 3.29\x*Nde Krais nt…®…®ri ma, Krais, ana Fhe Bak…®me ne ma. 
\c 4  
\s1 Guma Bak…®me, ana nduara won Ňčaara guma muuŇčgi Ňčaari ga suaŇčv ana suanga. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Ru 12.42; 1 Ko 3.5; 2 Ko 6.4; Ta 1.7; 1 Pi 4.10\x*Nza, nde kha nd…®knd…®gar muuŇčri, nza Kraisan Ňčaara gumgi ma. Fhe Bak…®me wo vhagi buni, ana nta bun suanga Ňčaarar nza n…®…®Ňčgi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Ru 12.42\x*Guma, ana harigi guman Ňčaara guma ki, ana tuituigira wo gari guma buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 3 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde gu mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv na suan za mbui o, maaŇč muuŇčgip, gumgi thari gu muuŇčgi bigi ga suaŇčv na suaŇčv suanga, gu ne suaŇč thaneŇč nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rver muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Gu vh…®ra, gu wo mbui t…®vi ga nzuav, wora nzuav nzuai fhuvara.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Jop 9.2; Sng 143.2; Snd 21.2; Ro 4.2\x*Guigi guarara, gu wo muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®k thueŇč kaŇčgi fhuvara. Gu vh…®ra khaŇč suanga fhu, ‚ÄúGu t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guma ma.‚ÄĚ Nan t…®vi ga suaŇčv na suanga Ňčaar, ana Guma Bak…®men Ňčaar ma.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Ro 2.1; 2.29; 1 Ko 3.8; 2 Ko 5.10; VB 20.12\x*Fhe Bak…®me nza khar mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv nza suanga tuk ntigar. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde fhumra harigi gumgi mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suaŇč thari. Nde Guma Bak…®me rarg…®ri, ana zir…®rga. Ana mba zorga g…®ng…®nan ki bigi, ana nta ndiv k…®rar vhava Ňčaara kh…®ngirga. Ana za mba gumgir nd…®knd…®gi ndiv k…®ra kh…®ngirga. Mba tugen nza bevbevira, Fhe Bak…®me nza muuŇčgi Ňčaari ga suaŇčv nzan ndikndigirga. 
\s1 Mbe KoriniŇč, mbe nduarira wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Ro 12.3; 1 Ko 1.12; 3.4; 3.21\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, gu nde nd…®knd…®gir kurkurar zav, Ňčka Aporos gum, gu Ňčka wani z…®ni zitav kha buni suaŇčgi. Nde Ňčka nd…®knd…®g…®p, nde Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gap suaŇčgi t…®vi guari, nde nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nde mba buni khiiŇč thiv…® thari. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde r…®…®Ňčr…®…®Ňčv guma the z…® ndi vun f…®v, the z…® mbev…® thari.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Zo 3.27; Ro 12.6; Ze 1.17; 1 Pi 4.10\x*Nde, the nde ndi fegim, nde z…®ri ki gumgi ki? Nde mba ntigem ndiga ki bigi Fhe Bak…®me nde n…®…®Ňčgi bigi ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, ne guigi guarara, nde Fhe Bak…®men harani panan mba bigi ndigi. Nde thaŇč nzuav wari won ŇčkasŇčkara mba bigi ndigi fara muuŇčgiap, nde wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi? 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt VB 3.17; 3.21\x*Ore, nde za mba bigir vhuuiŇč ndigap, nde za bigi tukt…®gi. Nde za mba bigi vhuuiŇč ndigap, nde guigira nzerara ki. Nde nza kambarigi. Nde nza kambarav Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani fara muuŇčgiap ki. Gu guigira nde Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani k…®rganen nde vuzvugi. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip k…®rim, nza vh…®ra nde phorg…®p, nza Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani k…®rga.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Ro 8.36; 1 Ko 15.30-31; 2 Ko 6.9; Hi 10.33\x*Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč nza muuŇčgi fhuvara. Gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Fhe Bak…®me, ana nza kha Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, ana nza ndiv z…® guarara t…®gi. Mbe nza nzuav suaŇčgim, mbe za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi gum Fhe Bak…®me enseri r…®mgi n…®man mbe nza shog…®rim, nza vh…®z…®rga.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt FG 26.24; 1 Ko 1.18; 3.18\x*Nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, nza nd…®knd…®k ki fhuv gumgi fara muuŇčgiap wari ki. Nde Zisas phorga kav, nde kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui nde nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč ki gumgir fara muuŇčgiap ki. Nza vh…®ra ŇčkasŇčkagi fhu, nde kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, nde ŇčkasŇčkagip wari ki. Nde kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, kha gumgi z…®ri bak…®vi nde nd…®…®v, nza z…®ri mbevi.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt FG 23.2; Ro 8.35; 2 Ko 11.23-27; Fi 4.12\x*Fhum kav zav ntigem, nza thi ndavira kav, nza mb…® nzuav fh…®ri khiav, nza shagi gori shari. Mbe vh…®ra nza shogim, nza tuituigip pera keg…®rga Ňčana thueŇč ki fhu, nza fhura tamtam kha Ňčanin vui.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Sng 109.28; Mt 5.44; FG 18.3; 1 Ko 9.14-15; 1 Te 2.9; 2 Te 3.8; 1 T 4.10\x*Nza guigira wari won farira Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbui. Mbe nza nz…®…®v nza nzuaim, nza mbe nzuai fhu, nza t…®var vhuun mben muun zav, mbe nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Mbe t…®va mbat…®gar nza mbui, nza fhura wari wo th…®…®ri p…®ngiap mba simt…®gi ndi.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Kra 3.45\x*Mbe nza z…®ri mbevav buni mbat…®gi guarira nza nzuaim, nza mbe buni Ňčgarkav mbarara bunin mbe nzuai. Nza kha gumgi gu mbigi r…®mgi n…®man, mbe nza garim, nza guigira mbat…®giap nzaŇčnzaŇčgi fara muuŇčgi. Nza za kha gumgi r…®mgi n…®man, nza bigi mbat…®gi fara muuŇčgiap guigira nzaŇčnzaŇčgi. Nza mbara muuŇčgiap kav, zav, ntige khar ki. 
\s1 Por khueŇč vuzvugi, KoriniŇč anan t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®rga. 
\p  
\v 14 Gu mem…®ran nden n…®…®n zav kha buni khergiap, nde ndi mbai fhuvara. Gu kha buni kheri, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nde nan tari ma. Gu guigira won ndavar nde nd…®…®i. Gu nde mba bigi kaŇčgir zav, gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap nde nd…®knd…®gi hiav nde nzuai. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip zazera Krais z…®n Ňčg…®rga.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt FG 18.11; Ga 4.19; Ze 1.18\x*Nde 10,000 gumgi kav, Kraisan t…®vir nde kh…®vav, nde gari, nde ndegi vh…®rve ki fhuvara. Krais Zisasan t…®vi ga nzuav, gu nduara nden ndia bavira. Gu Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuuen nde nzuai tugen, nde nan tari ga gegi.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt 1 Ko 11.1; Fi 3.17; 1 Te 1.6; 2 Te 3.9\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu khaŇč t…®gap nden nzuai, nde nan t…®vi gan…®v, nan t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt FG 19.22; Fi 2.19-22\x*Gu nera nzuav Timoti ga sararim, ana nde han z…®rga. Ana guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®gap, ana nan kama fara muuŇčgim, gu guigira won ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Gu ana khoth…®gi, ana tuituigiap Guma Bak…®men Ňčaara gari guma ma. Ana nde nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, nde gu Krais phorga havhargiap mbui t…®vi, nde nta nd…®knd…®g…®rga. Mba t…®vi, gu za kha Ňčguir ki siosir ki gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vi, mbe mba t…®vira z…®n Ňčg…®rga. 
\p  
\v 18 Nde thari khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, gu z…®v, nde gangirga fhuv thi? Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap fhura r…®…®r…®…®v ki.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt FG 18.21; 19.21; 1 Ko 16.5; 2 Ko 1.15; 1.23; Hi 6.3\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Guma Bak…®me na vuzvugirga, gu vhemkora nde han z…®g…®rga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip z…®g…®rga, gu mba r…®…®r…®…®i nt…®…®ri bunira mbarara zav zi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gu vh…®ra khueŇč nzuav gara zi, mbe ram mbui khesharigi ŇčkasŇčka ki.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 4:20 \xt 1 Ko 2.4; 1 Te 1.5\x*Fhe Bak…®me wo gumgi gu mbigi garim, mbe ana piin ki t…®v, ana ŇčkasŇčka ki big…®n ma, ana fhura kamthoon nzuai t…®vi fhuvara.  
\v 21 Nde vuzvugi, gu ram mbui khesharigi t…®var muuŇčrie? Ee, nde vuzvugi gu mpiiŇčs…®ga ndigi z…®v, nde th…®…® khar…®v, nde ndi th…®gar maaŇčrie? Ee, nde vuzvugi, gu ndavar nden n…®…®Ňčgip, nden korar muuŇčgip, z…®v, mbarara nden muuŇčrie? 
\c 5  
\ms1 Guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe wari r…®gar ki t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta ndiv th…®gar maaŇčri. 
\s1 Fhura ruarir mbigi gu gumgi, wari ndi t…®v KoriniŇč r…®gar ki 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Wkp 18.7-8; Lo 22.30; 27.20; Ef 5.3\x*Guigi guarara, gu mbararagim, mbe kha neŇčg…®a mbui, nde ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndi t…®va mbat…®ga guarara nden r…®gar ki. Mba Fhe Bak…®me guara rotu mbui fhuv gumgi, mbe vh…®ra mba khesharigi t…®va mbat…®ga mbui fhu. Mba t…®v khare, guma mbe, ana ruarir won ravar niamuuŇč ndiav ki.  
\v 2 Ndera mba t…®va garav, nde ne nzuav wari ndi vun kuamkuagi. Nde wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi t…®va thav, nde wari korar muuŇčv, wari ga suaŇčv nziri. Mba nden r…®gar kav mba t…®va mbat…®ga mbui guma, nde ana vhararim, ana nde thav sari. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Kor 2.5\x*KhueŇč guigi guarara, gu nde thav samra kim, nan vhen ki guma, ana nde phorga ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, gu guigira nde phorga ki. Gu nde phorga kav, mba t…®va mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi guma, gu ne ga nzuav ana suaŇčgi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Mt 16.19; 18.18; Zo 20.23; 2 Ko 13.10\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu khaŇč nzuai, nza wari wo Bak…®me Zisas z…®n panan nde phogar k…®rga, nza Bak…®me Zisasan ŇčkasŇčka nde phorg…® k…®rim, nan vhen ki guma, ana vh…®ra nde phorg…®p k…®rga.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt FG 26.18; 1 T 1.20; 1 Pi 4.6\x*Nde mba phogar k…®v, mba guma ndiv Satan farve kh…®ngirga, ana anan ndava vurar t…®vir farfagirga. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgirga, Guma Bak…®me taagip zir…®rga tugen, Fhe Bak…®me taagip mba guman tuma ndigirga. 
\s1 Mbe KoriniŇč, mbe t…®va mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi guma, mbe ana vhararim, ana mbe thav sari. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt 1 Ko 3.21; 15.33; Ga 5.9; Ze 4.16\x*Nde wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi, ne t…®var vhuuŇč fhuvara. Ee, ram muuŇčgi? Nde khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuve? Mba is bisanera, nera za mba viktuman muuŇčgirga, ana vhuuŇčgip k…®vgirga.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Kis 12.5; 12.21; 13.7; Ais 53.7; Zo 1.29; 1 Pi 1.19; VB 5.6; 5.12\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde za mba isa vur, nde zam ana ndi mbur sueg…®p, nde is ki fhuv viktuma kama farar muuŇčgip wari k…®ri. Gu nde kaŇčgi. Nde is ki fhuv viktuma fara muuŇčgiap wari ki. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mbe Krais shogiap, anan nde nzuav ofa muuŇčgi. Ana Pasova, tuga bak…®men shogiap, ofa mbui sipsiva fara muuŇčgi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Lo 16.3; Mt 16.6; 16.12; Ru 12.1\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nzan k…®r…® t…®vi, nta mba tuga bak…®men rotur muun zav bigi bevahegap ki gumgir farar muuŇčgip wari k…®ri. Nza mba harigi gumgi ga nzuav ndavi mbar…®gi t…®vi gum t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza zam nta thav, nta vhararim, nta nza thav sarim, nza guma mba tuga bak…®me nd…®knd…®gap, mba tuga bak…®me nzuav wo bigi bevahav wo phenan ki is vuri, ana zam nta ndiav nta fuasuegi fara muuŇčgi k…®ri. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip, nza ndavi vheri Ňčgaravra k…®v, guigira buni suanga. Mba t…®v, ana is ki fhuv viktuma kama farar muuŇčgip nzan k…®rga. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Mt 18.17; 2 Ko 6.14; Ef 5.11; 2 Te 3.14\x*Gu mba harigi gava khergiap nde ndi mbav, gu khaŇč nde suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúNde mba ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndi gumgi phorg…® ru thari.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Zo 17.15; 1 Ko 1.20; 10.27\x*Gu guigira za kha nuianan ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndi gumgi gum, bigi garav nta niihi gumgi gum, harigi gumgi bigi k…®…®i gumgi, gum mbar…®vi gu tori rotu mbui gumgi, gu za mbe thamthar zav nde nzuai fhuvara. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip za mba khesharigi gumgi, nde za mbe thamthar za mbui, nde za kha nuiana thav sari.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Mt 18.17; Ro 16.17; 2 Te 3.6; Ta 3.10; 2 Zo 1.10\x*Gu kha kameŇč khergi, ne n…®…®eŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Gu kha z…®n wari ga r…®gi gumgi, gu mbe nzuai. Mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu guigira Krais khoth…®gi.‚ÄĚ MaaŇč nzuai guma, ana ruarir mbigi ndi o, ana harigi gumgi bigi garav, nta niihi o, ana mbar…®vi gu tori rotu mbui o, ana harigi gumgi z…®rir farfagi o, ana pharar ŇčanŇčani pav o, ana harigi gumgi bigi k…®…®i, nde ana phorg…® ru thari. Nde vh…®ra mba khesharigi guma phorg…® mb…® thari.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Lo 13.5; 17.7; 21.21; 22.21-24; Mk 4.11; 1 Ko 6.1-4; Kor 4.5; 1 Te 4.12; 1 T 3.7\x*Gu ram muuŇčrie? Gu mba sios thav k…®rar ki gumgi, gu mbe mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga Ňčaara ndigire? Fhuvara! Mba sios vhen ki gumgi, mbe mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga Ňčaar, ana nden Ňčaara guar ma.  
\v 13 Mba sios thav k…®rar ki gumgi, Fhe Bak…®me nduara mbe mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mba guma mbat…®k nden r…®gar ki, nde ana vhararim, ana nde thav sari.‚ÄĚ 
\c 6  
\s1 Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde sios vhen ki gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv suaŇčri. 
\p  
\v 1 Nde guigira khaŇč muuŇč thari. Nden r…®gar ki guma the, ana guma the suaŇčv suan saŇčv ana Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi khara th…®g…® Ňčg…®p, Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi r…®mgi n…®man ana suaŇčv suaŇč thari. Ana mba t…®var muungen mbergirga fhuv thi?  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Dan 7.22; Mt 19.28; VB 2.26; 3.21; 20.4\x*Nde khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuv thi? Nza Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, nza zumgum kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga. Nza maaŇč muunga, nde thaŇč nzuav kha nden r…®gar h…®gi simt…®gi bisarire, nde nta suaŇč wari ga suangeŇč thagire?  
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt 2 Pi 2.4; Zu 1.6\x*Nde vh…®ra khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuve? Nza Fhe Bak…®me enseri t…®vi ga suaŇčv vh…®ra mbe suanga. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza vh…®ra kha nuiana simt…®gi, nza nta suaŇčv suanga tukt…®gi.  
\v 4 MaaŇč muuŇčgip simt…®ga thueŇč nden r…®gar h…®g…®rga, nde thaŇč nzuav mba simt…®geŇč ga suan zav, sios thav k…®rar ki gumgi ga nzuai?  
\v 5 Gu nde mber…®r zav, gu khuen nde nzuai. Ee, nden sios vhen ki gumgi r…®gar nd…®knd…®k vhuuŇč ki guma the ki fhuve? Ana k…®v nden sios vhen h…® simt…®gi ndiv th…®gar maanga.  
\v 6 Nde thav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma mbe, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma mbe muuŇčgi simt…®geŇč ga nzuav, ana ndiga vov, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhu gumgi n…®man ana nzuav nzuai. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt Mt 5.39; Snd 20.22; Ru 6.29; Ro 12.17-19; 1 Te 5.15; 1 Pi 3.9\x*Nde sios vhen ki gumgi gu mbigi mbari ndiga vov, mbe nzuav nzuai. Nde maaŇč mbuav, nde regap, nde Krais t…®vi z…®n vui fhuvara. Nde fhura mbe gan…®rim, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi nden muunga, ne guigira nzerarga. Nde vh…®ra fhura mbe gan…®rim, mbe nde bigi k…®m…®nga, ne guigira nzerarga.  
\v 8 Nde kha t…®vir vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…® thagi. Nde vh…®ra t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, nde wari t…®n wari wo bigi k…®…®i. Nde mba t…®va mbuav, nde phorga guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde ne mbera mbui. 
\p  
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 6:9-10 \xt Ga 5.19-21; Ef 5.5; 1 T 1.9; Hi 12.14; VB 22.15\x*Mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me wo gumgi garim, mbe ana piin ki nt…®…®ri phorg…® keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde ne kaŇčgi fhuve? Nde nduarira wari won ndavi vheri guiguigi thari. Kha t…®va mbui gumgi, ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndi gumgi, mbar…®vi gu tori rotu mbui gumgi, mani ga r…®gi mbigi phorga t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mbark…®rga mberi t…®vi mbat…®gi gumgi ntan harigi gumgi phorga mbui, k…®…®i gumgi, harigi gumgi bigi garav nta niihi gumgi, zazera phara ŇčanŇčani pi gumgi, harigi gumgi z…®ri mbevi gumgi, harigi gumgi bigi Ňčgi gumgi, mba khesharigi gumgi zam, mbe Fhe Bak…®me wo gumgi garim, mbe ana piin ki nt…®…®ri phorg…® keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Ef 2.2; Kor 3.7; Ta 3.3-7; Hi 10.22\x*Nde mbari fhum mba khesharigi t…®vi ga mbui gumgi kegi. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap kim, Fhe Bak…®me nde ndigap, nde ruagim, nde ana gumgi gu mbigi guari ki. Nde ntigem, Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais, nde ana z…®n panan, nde Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ŇčkasŇčkar panan, Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgim, nde ntigem ana r…®mani n…®man, nde t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ki. 
\s1 Nzan fhavi, nta Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaarar phen ma. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Ko 10.23\x*Gumgi mbari, mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu za kha bigi ga mbui, ne nzerara.‚ÄĚ Mba kameŇč, ne guigira. Mba bigi, nta za nden kurarim, nde nzerara keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Gu za mba bigir muunga, ne nzerara. Gu fhura mba big…®n the gan…®rim, ana na gan…®nga tukt…®gi fhuvara.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Ro 14.17; 1 Ko 6.15; 15.19-20; Kor 2.22-23; 1 Te 4.3-7\x*Gumgi mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba, nta ndava mbuim, ana givi bigi ma. Ndav, ana mba nzuav ki ne ma.‚ÄĚ Mba kameŇč, ne guigi guarara. Fhe Bak…®me, ana mbark…®rga mba, ana ntan vh…®z…®v, ana vh…®ra nzan ndavi, ana vh…®ra nta vh…®zgirga. Nzan fhavi, nta ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndir zav Fhe Bak…®me nta muuŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nzan fhavi, nta Guma Bak…®me Ňčaara mbui fhavi ma. Guma Bak…®me, ana nzan fhavi gari.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Ro 6.5; 6.8; 8.11; 1 Ko 15.20; 2 Ko 4.14; Ef 1.19-20\x*Fhe Bak…®me won ŇčkasŇčkara Guma Bak…®me rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgi. Ana vh…®ra nza khavgirga. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Ro 12.5; 1 Ko 12.27; Ef 4.12; 4.16; 5.30\x*Ee, nde khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuv thi? Nde fhavi nta Kraisan fhavir f…®giveiŇč ma? MaaŇč muuŇčgip, gu Kraisan fhava thueŇč ndigip nen ruarir gumgi ndi mbigar fhava phorg…®rga, ne t…®var vhuuŇč ee? Zak…®ra fhuvara!  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Stt 2.24; Mt 19.5; Ef 5.31\x*Guma, ana ruarir gumgi ndi mbiga phorgi, ana ana phorgap, mani fhava bavira ki. Ee, nde ne kaŇčgi fhuv thi? Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMani wani t…®gap fhava bavira ki.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Zo 17.21-23; Ro 8.9-11; Ef 4.4\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma ana Guma Bak…®me phorgi, ana vhen ki guma ana phorgap, mani guma bavira ki.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt Ro 1.24; 6.12-13; 1 Te 4.3; Hi 13.4\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndi t…®va thav r…®…®v Ňčg…®p samra k…®ri. Mba harigi t…®vi mbat…®gi zam, gumgi nta mbui nta gumgi k…®rar wari won fhavi ndirar mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi ma. Guma ana ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndi, ana t…®va mbat…®gar won fhavara mbui.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 6:19 \xt Ro 14.7-8; 1 Ko 3.16; 2 Ko 6.16\x*Ee, nde khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuv thi? Ndun fhav, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaarar phen ma. Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar nde n…®…®Ňčgim, ana nden vhen ki. Ndun fhav, ana ndu ne fhuvara.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 6:20 \xt 1 Ko 7.23; Ga 3.13; Fi 1.20; Hi 9.12; 1 Pi 1.18-19\x*Zak…®ra fhuvara! Fhe Bak…®me vheza bak…® guarara ndu vhezgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu wo fhavar mbui bigi, ndu Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuav mba bigir muuŇčri. 
\c 7  
\ms1 Por mani gu muuiŇč wari ga r…®gi ne nzuai. 
\s1 Por mani gu muuiŇč wari ga r…®gi ne nzuai. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt 1 Ko 7.8; 7.26\x*Gu ntigem nde mba gavar khergi kameŇč, gu ne Ňčgarkar za mbui. Guma, ana muuaŇč t…®gi fhu, ne nzerara.  
\v 2 Ne nzerara, ntigem ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndi t…®v guigira k…®vgim, maaŇč muuŇčgiap khaŇč muuŇčgirga, ne nzerarga. Gumgi bevbevira, mbe won muuŇčra hiari. Mbigi vh…®ra, mbe bevbevira, mbe won manira hiari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Kis 21.10; 1 Pi 3.7\x*Guma, ana fhav, ana ana muun fhav ma. Ana won fhavar won muuŇč ga kirp…®g…® thari. Mba t…®vara, ana muun fhav, ana ana mana ne ma, ana won fhavar won mana kirp…®g…® thari.  
\v 4 Mbik, ana nduara wo fhava gari fhuvara. Anan man, ana ana fhava gari guma ma. Mba t…®vara, ana man, ana vh…®ra ana nduara wo fhava gari fhuvara. Anan muuŇč, ana ana fhava gari mbik ma.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt Jol 2.16; Sek 7.3; 1 Te 3.5\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip, mani gu muuiŇč warir r…®gip, nde k…®r wari ga s…®v, the won fhavar the kirp…®g…® thari. KhueŇč guigira, Ňčko maaŇč muuŇčgip wani ga suaŇčgip ndava bavira k…®v, tuga t…®vaneŇčra Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suan saŇčv wani phorg…® ku thamtharga, ne nzerara. Ňäko maaŇč muuŇčgip, Ňčko zumgum wom wani phorg…® kuri. Ňäko muuŇčv k…®v, Ňčko nuanira tuituigip wani won vuzvugi gan…®nga fhuv, Satan z…®v Ňčkon mpararim, Ňčko r…®g…®rga.  
\v 6 Kha buneŇč, nde khaŇč suaŇč thari, tha mbe ma, nza mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®rga, fhuvara. Gu nden kurkurar zav, gu kha buneŇč nzuai.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 7:7 \xt Mt 19.12; FG 26.29; 1 Ko 12.11\x*Gu vuzvugi, kha mbigi gu gumgi, mbe zam nan farar muuŇčgip s…®…®Ňčra k…®rga. Fhe Bak…®me za kha gumgi bevbevira, ana mbark…®rga nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč gum Ňčaarir muun zav ŇčkasŇčkagir mbe n…®…®Ňčgi. Guma mbe, ana nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč gum ŇčkasŇčka mben ana n…®…®Ňčgiap, harigi ne, ana harigi nd…®knd…®gar vhuuŇč gum ŇčkasŇčka ana n…®…®Ňčgi. 
\p  
\v 8 Mba s…®…®Ňčra ki gumgi gu mbigi, mba mani vh…®zgi s…®…®Ňčra ki mbigi, gu khaŇč mbe nzuai. Mbe nan farar muuŇčgip s…®…®Ňčra k…®rga, ne nzerara.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt 1 T 5.14\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip k…®v, mbe tuituigi wari won vuzvugi gari fhuv, mbe mani gu muuiŇč r…®g…®ri. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgirga, ne nzerarga. Mbe fhura k…®rga, mbe ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari ndirga ne suaŇčv z…®gz…®g…® rivgi. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 7:10 \xt Mal 2.14-16\x*\x - \xo 7:10 \xt Mt 5.32; 19.9; Mk 10.11-12; Ru 16.18\x*Mba mani gu muuiŇč ga r…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, gu kha t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®r zav mba t…®var mbe nd…®…®i. Mba t…®v, gu nduara nzuai t…®v fhuvara. Ana Guma Bak…®me z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nzuai t…®v ma. Mba t…®v khaŇč nzuai, mbik mana t…®gi, ana won mana thamtha thari.  
\v 11 Ana wo mana thagi, ana s…®…®Ňčra k…®ri. Ana s…®…®Ňčra keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara, ana taagip wo mana phorg…®p ndava bavira k…®v, ana taagip Ňčg…®p wo mana phorg…® k…®ri. Mba t…®vara, guma vh…®ra, ana won muuŇč thamtha thari. 
\p  
\v 12 Gu nduara, gu buna muen mba wari ga r…®giavra ki nt…®…®rir ki. Khe Guma Bak…®me suaŇčgi buneŇč fhuvara. Gu khaŇč nzuai. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma the mbiga the t…®gi, ana mba t…®gi mbik guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhu, mba mbik won mana vuzvugira k…®rim, ana man ana thamtha thari.  
\v 13 Mbik vh…®ra, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhuv guma the t…®gi, mba guma, ana vuzvugira k…®rim, mba mbik ana thamtha thari.  
\v 14 Gu khaŇč muuŇčgiap ne nzuai, guma, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhu, ana muuŇč guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, ana ana phorga kim, Fhe Bak…®me ana garim, ana anan guma mbe fara muuŇčgi. Mbik, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhu, ana man guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, ana ana phorga kim, Fhe Bak…®me ana garim, ana anan mbiga mbe fara muuŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nden tari ntigem Fhe Bak…®me mbe gari. Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgirga fhu, mben tari mbe Fhe Bak…®men khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi gu mbigir tari farar muuŇčgip k…®rga.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 7:15 \xt Ro 12.18; 14.19; Hi 12.14\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma o mbik guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhu, anan muuŇč o man guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, ana ana thamtha za mbui, ana fhura ana gan…®rim, ana Ňčg…®ri. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mba t…®v h…®rga, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma o mbik maaŇč muuŇčgip guigira Zisas khoth…®gi fhuv guma o mbiga t…®gi, mani b…®nan ki fara muuŇčgi fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me nza wari t…®g…®p ndava bavira k…®r zav nzan kamgi.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 7:16 \xt 1 Pi 3.1\x*Ndu mbik, ndu won manan kurarim, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®rga o, fhu. Ndu ne kaŇčgi fhu. Ndu guma, ndu won muun kurarim, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®rga o, fhu? Ndu vh…®ra ne kaŇčgi fhu. 
\s1 Nza Fhe Bak…®me nzan mbuigi k…®r…® t…®vir k…®rga. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt 1 Ko 4.17; 7.20; 7.24\x*Nde bevbevira Guma Bak…®me Zisas nzan mbuigi k…®r…® t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®v k…®rga. Nde ram muuŇčgi k…®r…® t…®var kim, Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgim, nde mba k…®r…® t…®va k…®rga. Gu kha t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®r zav mba t…®var za kha siosi ga n…®…®Ňčgi.  
\v 18 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the mbe ana fooŇčgirim, Fhe Bak…®me zumgum ana kamgirim, mba guma mbe ana fooŇčgi ne ndi zomzor…®v wom wo fhava nder ndi th…®gar maaŇč thari. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the mbe ana fooŇčgi fhu, Fhe Bak…®me ana kamgi, ana won fooŇč thari.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 7:19 \xt Zo 15.14; Ro 2.25; Ga 5.6; 6.15\x*Fooi t…®v, ana fhura ki t…®v ma. Fooi fhuv t…®v, ana vh…®ra fhura ki t…®v ma. Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n vui t…®v, ana guigira big…®na guar ma.  
\v 20 Nza ram muuŇčgi k…®r…® t…®var kim, Fhe Bak…®me nzan kamgi, nza mba k…®r…® t…®vara k…®ri.  
\v 21 Ee, ndu fhura Ňčaara guma gum Ňčaara mbiga kh…®n kim, Fhe Bak…®me ndu kamgire? Ndu ne suaŇčv ndav sim…® thari. Ndu b…®kb…®…®gip k…®rga tuav k…®ri, ndu mba tuav z…®n Ňčg…®ri.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 7:22 \xt Zo 8.36; Ga 5.13; Ef 6.6; Fm 1.16; 1 Pi 2.16\x*Guma ana fhura Ňčaara kh…®nan muuŇčv k…®rim, Guma Bak…®me ana kamgirga, ana ntigem Guma Bak…®me guma ma. Ana ntigem, Guma Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man, ana wom Ňčaara guma kh…®n ki fhuvara. Mba t…®vara, guma ana b…®kb…®…®gip kim, Guma Bak…®me ana kamgi, ana ntigem fhura Kraisan Ňčgari Ňčaara guma kh…®n ki.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 7:23 \xt 1 Ko 6.20; 1 Pi 1.18-19\x*Fhe Bak…®me, ana guigira vheza bak…® guarara nde vhezgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde fhura harigi gumgir vuzvugi z…®n Ňčg…®p mben Ňčaari gumgi kh…®ni k…® thari.  
\v 24 Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde ram muuŇčgi khesharigi k…®r…® t…®var kim, Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgim, nde mba khesharigi k…®r…® t…®vara muuŇčv k…®ri. 
\s1 Por nz…®ri gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai buni khare. 
